format_rule:
Respond in JSON format like this:
{{
  "detected": true/false,
  "highlights": ["list of text fragments to highlight from the message (or empty if none)"],
  "weaknesses": ["Short summary in a couple of words for each detected weaknesses.(empty of none)."],
  "highlight_indices": [[start_index, end_index], ...]  (list of index pairs or empty list if none).
}}
